---
title: Squash Ravioli and Shrimp in Leek Sauce with Candied-Chili Walnuts
description: Pillowy soft butternut squash stuffed ravioli is tossed in a savoury leek and spinach sauce topped with shrimp and a sprinkle of smoky candied walnuts for barely there heat and sweet crunch!
